name: Happy Valentine's Day 2022
description:
Happy Valentine's Day to the beautiful and talented Tezos community! 

This is my first Tezos erotic art, a reminder that regardless if you're in a relationship or not, the one of the most important love and affection you can give yourself, is self-love

Self-love is beautiful and can manifest in anyway, from self-pleasure, to maybe taking yourself out on a self-date by going out to dinner on your own or staying in and making a day to please yourself, it doesn't matter, as long as it's genuine and feels good to you.

You're beautiful just the way you are and that's what makes this community so amazing <3

-Much love, 
Neo
